MERGE [WholePrices] USING (
VALUES (@p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, 0),
(@p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 1)) AS i ([FromQuantity], [Price], [ProductId], [ToQuantity], _Position) ON 1=0

OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted1;
